# ec7c6c65d7c341a69ad994104f9b0fe0
#: ../../admin-guide/monitoring/logging/managing-logs.en.rst:176
msgid ""
"Log files are rolled at specific intervals relative to a given hour of "
"the day. Three options may be used to control when log files are rolled:"
msgstr ""

